Function to recode water indicators for WASH for the Myanmar MCCT Programme Evaluation Survey

Source: R/07-recode_wash.R
recode_water.Rd

Function to recode water indicators for WASH for the Myanmar MCCT Programme Evaluation Survey

recode_water(df)

Arguments

df

A data.frame collected for the Myanmar MCCT Programme Evaluation Study containing water, sanitation and hygiene data

Value

A vector of recoded water indicators

Examples

recode_water(df = hh)
